issuer.name: Hyland Credentials
issuer.description: Hyland partners with governments, companies, and school systems to deploy secure credentialing systems that leverage the blockchain as a secure anchor of trust. To ensure the longevity and interoperability of these records, we are ongoing contributors to standards communities, including Blockcerts, IMS Global, and the W3C.

signatureLines.jobTitle: Chris Jagers, General Manager Hyland Credentials
